snippet.title: Big Sea gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Big Sea (aka big sea: the better one will win), Dos PC game produced by Starbyte in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/big-sea/6220/
Exploring the interface in this bizarre and quirky strategy adventure game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
